{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"3532","text":"The scheme has serious deficiencies","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:26"},{"nodeID":"3533","text":"The insured will complain for the increase","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:26"},{"nodeID":"3534","text":"The goverment could not afford the discount","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:26"},{"nodeID":"3535","text":"The goal of the scheme is highly subject to failure","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:26"},{"nodeID":"3536","text":"For example who is to tell whether someone is dropping into their health club for coffee and to read a newspaper rather than to take exercise","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:26"},{"nodeID":"3537","text":"Julian Crooks an independent financial adviser told BBC News Online","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:26"},{"nodeID":"3538","text":"the costs of monitoring people's fitness will ultimately be passed onto consumers through higher premiums","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3539","text":"If the premium increses the insured persons will complain for that","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3540","text":"the 25% discount given to all policyholders after one year suggested the scheme could be too expensive to start with.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3541","text":"If a discount is too high the government could not afford it","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3542","text":"In addition Mr Crooks said that he was concerned that the scheme could be abused.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3543","text":"If the scheme can be abused its goal can fail","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3544","text":"I question whether it can be proved 100% that people are making the strides that are being rewarded for","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3545","text":"If it cannot be proved that people are making the strides that are being rewarded for the scheme can be abused","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27"},{"nodeID":"3546","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27","scheme":"Example"},{"nodeID":"3547","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:27","scheme":"Example"},{"nodeID":"3548","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:28","scheme":"Example"},{"nodeID":"3549","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:28","scheme":"Example"},{"nodeID":"3550","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:28","scheme":"ExpertOpinion"},{"nodeID":"3551","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:29","scheme":"CauseToEffect"},{"nodeID":"3552","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:29","scheme":"CauseToEffect"},{"nodeID":"3553","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:29","scheme":"CauseToEffect"},{"nodeID":"3554","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 18:29:30","scheme":"CauseToEffect"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"3351","fromID":"3533","toID":"3546","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3352","fromID":"3546","toID":"3532","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3353","fromID":"3534","toID":"3547","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3354","fromID":"3547","toID":"3532","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3355","fromID":"3535","toID":"3548","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3356","fromID":"3548","toID":"3532","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3357","fromID":"3536","toID":"3549","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3358","fromID":"3549","toID":"3545","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3359","fromID":"3537","toID":"3550","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3360","fromID":"3550","toID":"3532","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3361","fromID":"3538","toID":"3551","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3362","fromID":"3539","toID":"3551","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3363","fromID":"3551","toID":"3533","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3364","fromID":"3540","toID":"3552","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3365","fromID":"3541","toID":"3552","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3366",